Description: cqh_file_watcher
        =============================================
        
        something like `File-Watcher` for vscode
        
        
        ## Usage
        -------------------------------------------------
        
        `cqh-file-watch -c ***.conf`
        
        ### conf example
        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
        
        
        .. code-block::
        
            {"command_list":[
                {
                    "pattern": "*.py",
                    "command": "sudo supervisorctl restart redis"
                },
                {
                    "command": "echo things changed"
                }
            ]
            "directory": "/home/vagrant/code/code1"
            }
        
